cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the development of an algorithm for open-ended machine learning, which involves generating and solving novel challenges. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The algorithm also involves reinforcement learning (cs.RO) and system engineering (cs.SY) to optimize its performance. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a domain-general measure to evaluate the novelty of challenges, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
